{"tid":1655324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】歐盟報告揭林鄭稱「與暴徒談判無意義」 企硬拒重啟政改","createTime":"2019-10-15T04:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T05:55:25.000Z","uid":217430,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"69273fc68279a19e329f806d7a8a0909a5dd2be0","tid":1655324,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"今日《南華早報》引述歐盟內部報告，指行政長官林鄭月娥早前與歐盟駐香港及澳門代表Carmen Cano會面，指目前重新展開關於普選的討論不可行（Not feasible to relaunch a debate on universal suffrage now），又指回應示威者訴求毫無意義，因為「你沒法跟暴徒談判（you can't negotiate with the mob）」。林鄭今早出席行政會議前回應事件，揶揄「而家洩漏風氣好犀利」，指出有關報告不是她撰寫，但確認曾與歐盟代表會面，她未有正面回應是否曾與代表講述有關言論，但就回應當中有關區議會的內容，強調希望區議會選舉可順利進行。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述林鄭與歐盟代表會面，對於坊間的五大訴求之一是重啟政改，她指重啟政改是需要全國人大進行的憲法過程，而社會出現兩極化，故目前將難以進行有關討論。曾稱希望與聽取市民訴求，但曾進行一場公開論壇後便再無舉辦，報告引述林鄭指現時回應示威者訴求沒有意義（pointless），因為「你沒法跟暴徒談判（you can't negotiate with the mob）」強調示威者近日蓄意破壞和堵路行為。而明日發表的施政報告，林鄭月娥表示將會側重於土地和住房問題，她又重申對「一國兩制」的信心，但不會談及政治問題。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指林鄭承認在即將舉行的區議會選舉中，建制派將會遭受重大挫敗，但強調會確保區議會選舉如期於11月24日舉行，不過就要視乎示威者（But it was &quot;up to protesters&quot;）。林鄭月娥今早出席行會前承認曾於上周與歐盟主管Carmen Cano見面，相信有關報告是歐盟辦公室去寫，但就拒評有關內容，僅稱有決心去辦區議會選舉，因是香港政治體制重要的一環，雖然是諮詢架構，但亦是非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60154972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60154972&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9P%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=69accba8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60154972&h=f86bf728\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60154972</a>"},{"pid":"04ebfa0a7fcda2ed433c96fadaafba33f668376e","tid":1655324,"uid":217430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"又指回應示威者訴求毫無意義，因為「你沒法跟暴徒談判（you can't negotiate with the mob）」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">說好的對話平台？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c5102ec93a175a85b08ff52e4b038d520531ea","tid":1655324,"uid":91914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"條7婆仲係咁口硬"},{"pid":"d5f2cd820a753ddfc304c3780a4635cc96d477d5","tid":1655324,"uid":214192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04ebfa0a7fcda2ed433c96fadaafba33f668376e","tid":1655324,"uid":217430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"又指回應示威者訴求毫無意義，因為「你沒法跟暴徒談判（you can't negotiate with the mob）」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">說好的對話平台？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:15:29.000Z","msg":"做show囉"},{"pid":"a62aaf05d2be1e3a2335c3e61e1eeef1fa707fc3","tid":1655324,"uid":33471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"柒啦 開會落左minute既野 係未正式出之前你覺得唔係你所講既野就提出啦<br />\n<br />\nreport都出埋仲係度撐話唔代表自己"},{"pid":"09b68e37bb4b801aa1aedd42989fd3bb7c17ceda","tid":1655324,"uid":38305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"自認好打得又點會投降"},{"pid":"d2786269215ef572906e9f7e67d5a97fa0a48f07","tid":1655324,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"好呀 日日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be69216ecb1b58b5cdb15d92ae06b425fdd8f371","tid":1655324,"uid":217430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"林鄭今早出席行政會議前回應事件，揶揄<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「而家洩漏風氣好犀利」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚柒串。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a786bf0ea6f56d9adfd743ae4638f9c13220875","tid":1655324,"uid":281401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"港共深得中共既鬥爭本領，林鄭這句話的意思是：香港發生的抗爭，不是人民內部矛盾，是敵我矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n兩者的分別是，人民內部矛盾能夠透過對話、協商、讓步來解決，因為當權者會視抗爭者為自己的人民；敵我矛盾，則完全沒有任何的對話空間，因為對方是敵人，只可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">殲滅</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n這一點，是香港人應該加以對外宣傳。香港林鄭政權跟香港人，差不多已經成了兩個陣營。"},{"pid":"7b981067c29456521752eca0aaca40002a36563a","tid":1655324,"uid":322955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04ebfa0a7fcda2ed433c96fadaafba33f668376e","tid":1655324,"uid":217430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"又指回應示威者訴求毫無意義，因為「你沒法跟暴徒談判（you can't negotiate with the mob）」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">說好的對話平台？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"不抗議就硬過送中<br />\n抗議就說你港獨暴徒，拒絕談判<br />\n<br />\n龍門任你搬耶"},{"pid":"f771539d1ea840ebc5d06dbb5bba34af11329f1b","tid":1655324,"uid":116967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"條柒婆真係唔驚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.